<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Join Request</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #111;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: #000;
            position: relative;
        }
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header-left {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 50px;
        }
        .logo-name {
            margin-left: 10px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .avatar {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 50%;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 2px;
            background-color: #444;
        }
        .details {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .status {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #bbb;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #bbb;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-left">
                <img src="https://astronex.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/system/494ed628-4978-4a87-9dff-0f01e4109b53-astronex_logo.jpeg" alt="Astronex Logo" class="logo">
                <span class="logo-name">Astronex</span>
            </div>
            <img src="{{avatar}}" alt="User Avatar" class="avatar">
        </div>
        <h2>Hey {{memberName}},</h2>
        <h3>We have received your join request!</h3>
        <div class="details">
            <p>Your Request to join <strong>{{instituteName}}</strong> institute is on <span class="status">{{status}}</span> status right now.</p>
        </div>
        <p>The institute will check your details and process your join request. We appreciate your patience.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© 2024 Astronex Community</p>
            <p><a href="mailto:noreply@astronex.com">noreply@astronex.com</a> | <a href="http://www.astronex.org">www.astronex.org</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
